Ideation Phase:

Project Title: Optimizing User, Group, and Role Management with Access Control & Workflows in ServiceNow

Idea Summary:
This project improves how organizations manage users, groups, and roles.
With ServiceNow, we make access control easier, faster, and more secure through automation.

Why this idea?
✅ Better security
✅ Less manual work
✅ Fast access permission changes

Goal of the Project:
To create an automated system in ServiceNow for:
	•	Default role assignment
	•	Workflow approvals
	•	Secure access control
